README.extra: This is the extra directory README file.

Directory is part of Guide to Installing and Setting Up an Overpass Server on
Slackware64 15.0 repository.

Directory contains scripts and configuration files not provided by overpass.
Included total of 8 files listed here:

op_initial.sh
op_update_db.sh
rc.dispatcher
op_ctl.sh
cron4op.sh
httpd-overpass.conf
op_logrotate
README.extra
